text: A. K. M. Shamsul Haque is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Kishoreganj-1. ==Career== Haque was elected to parliament from Kishoreganj-1 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1996. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:1999 deaths Category:7th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: A. K. M. Shamsul Haque
